# Paper-to-Plugin Skill

This skill analyzes a research paper, extracts key innovations, and generates a Python plugin package based on them.

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

```bash
paper-to-plugin <path_or_url_to_paper> --output-dir <directory_for_generated_plugin>
```
